data.description: Cutie Pie of a House in an Impeccable Location! This 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home is nestled on 3/4 of an acre in the middle of Mauldin/Greenville metropolitan area. Property is very closely located to I 85. Home features double living spaces. Yard currently houses livestock. Don't miss out on your opportunity at this diamond in the rough.
